	"<h2 id=\"curated-excellence-gifted-with-purpose\">Curated Excellence, Gifted with Purpose</h2>\n<p>Our premium gift sets are thoughtfully curated collections designed to impress. Whether it’s for executive appreciation, client milestones, or festive celebrations, each set tells a story of quality and care.</p>\n<h3 id=\"featured-collections\">Featured Collections</h3>\n<h4 id=\"executive-collection\">Executive Collection</h4>\n<p>The pinnacle of corporate gifting. Includes premium leather goods, high-end writing instruments, and luxury accessories — all beautifully presented in a magnetic closure gift box.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Premium leather cardholder or wallet</li>\n<li>Parker or Cross metal pen set</li>\n<li>Silk pocket square or branded tie</li>\n<li>Personalized engraved nameplate</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"tech-enthusiast-set\">Tech Enthusiast Set</h4>\n<p>For the modern professional. A curated selection of the latest tech accessories.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Wireless charging pad with LED logo</li>\n<li>Premium Bluetooth earbuds</li>\n<li>Branded power bank (10,000mAh)</li>\n<li>Custom cable organizer pouch</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"eco-friendly-collection\">Eco-Friendly Collection</h4>\n<p>Show your commitment to sustainability with our earth-conscious gift sets.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bamboo tumbler with branded sleeve</li>\n<li>Recycled cotton tote bag</li>\n<li>Plantable seed paper notebook</li>\n<li>Organic cotton t-shirt (branded)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"welcome-kit\">Welcome Kit</h4>\n<p>Perfect for onboarding new employees or welcoming new clients.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Branded notebook and pen set</li>\n<li>Company tumbler or mug</li>\n<li>Custom lanyard and ID holder</li>\n<li>Welcome letter with branded stationery</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"customization-options\">Customization Options</h3>\n<p>Every gift set can be customized to match your needs:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Product selection</strong>: Mix and match items from our catalog</li>\n<li><strong>Branding</strong>: Add your logo to every item in the set</li>\n<li><strong>Packaging</strong>: Choose from our signature boxes or custom designs</li>\n<li><strong>Personal touches</strong>: Include handwritten notes or personalized items</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"pricing\">Pricing</h3>\n<p>Our premium gift sets start from Rp 150.000 per set (minimum 25 sets). Volume discounts apply for orders above 100 sets. Contact us for a custom quote tailored to your budget and requirements.</p>\n",
